{"tid":1202364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"999熱線去年接逾200萬來電　三分一屬滋擾打錯　警籲勿濫用","createTime":"2019-06-11T08:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:40:59.000Z","uid":37757,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7e84d3e908705e1c80813ab486bb38e4543efc","tid":1202364,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"警方公布，2018年各總區指揮及控制中心共接聽2,187,619個來電，當中只有1,456,853個、約66.6%為需要處理的求助電話，其餘730,766個來電屬滋擾性或錯誤撥出。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">濫用緊急熱線會延誤警方處理有真正需要個案，令市民生命安全受到威脅，呼籲應在緊急情況下才致電999緊急服務中心</span></span></strong>，切勿濫用；市民有需要時，可直接向警署求助。<br />\n<br />\n各警署電話可瀏覽警隊網站或查閱「香港警隊流動應用程式」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190131/s00001/1548919599269/999%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%9A%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%80%BE200%E8%90%AC%E4%BE%86%E9%9B%BB-%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E5%B1%AC%E6%BB%8B%E6%93%BE%E6%89%93%E9%8C%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190131%2Fs00001%2F1548919599269%2F999%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%259B%25BB-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%25BB%258B%25E6%2593%25BE%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%258C%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E5%258B%25BF%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=8c19b3e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190131%2Fs00001%2F1548919599269%2F999%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%259B%25BB-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E6%25